content: I ordered from BurgerFi, Sweetfin Poké, and El Torito Grill from UberEats, and I really liked the Korean BBQ tacos from Sweetfin Poké. As for dietary restrictions, I'm pretty open to trying anything, but I do try to eat healthy and save money by meal prepping on Sundays. I've been making quinoa and roasted veggies, and experimenting with overnight oats recipes.
